00:20:08.480 --> 00:20:09.980
&gt;&gt; Diane Rehm: We hope it happens.

00:20:09.980 --> 00:20:12.840
&gt;&gt; David M. Rubenstein: So
when you are an interviewer one

00:20:12.840 --> 00:20:15.470
