00:23:23.910 --> 00:23:31.330
which is a problem whose
origins they have no clue on.

00:23:31.330 --> 00:23:36.110
It begins in the vassal
ganglia of the brain.

00:23:36.110 --> 00:23:44.850 position:56%
The vassal ganglia informs the vocal
cords to clamp down inappropriately.

00:23:44.850 --> 00:23:47.380
There is no known cause.

00:23:47.380 --> 00:23:50.520
There is no known cure.

00:23:50.520 --> 00:23:53.740
But there is a treatment

00:23:53.740 --> 00:23:58.250
and I received an injection
of Botox that very day.

00:23:58.250 --> 00:24:00.750
&gt;&gt; David M. Rubenstein: So Botox
which is, you know, very -- .

00:24:00.750 --> 00:24:02.050
&gt;&gt; Diane Rehm: Poison.

00:24:02.050 --> 00:24:03.350
&gt;&gt; David M. Rubenstein: Poison.

00:24:03.350 --> 00:24:04.820
They gave you a little bit of it

00:24:04.820 --> 00:24:08.940
and they told you it would probably
take away your voice for a while.

00:24:08.940 --> 00:24:10.620
