00:27:01.980 --> 00:27:06.650
But you had a relationship
with your husband for 52 years.

00:27:06.650 --> 00:27:07.950
&gt;&gt; Diane Rehm: Fifty-four.

00:27:07.950 --> 00:27:09.250
&gt;&gt; David M. Rubenstein:
Fifty-four years.

00:27:09.250 --> 00:27:10.550
&gt;&gt; Diane Rehm: Mm-hmm.

00:27:10.550 --> 00:27:11.850
&gt;&gt; David M. Rubenstein:
So what happened

00:27:11.850 --> 00:27:14.980
to your husband's health
a few years ago?

00:27:14.980 --> 00:27:20.850
&gt;&gt; Diane Rehm: After he
retired from the practice

00:27:20.850 --> 00:27:25.940
of international law
he began waiting for me

00:27:25.940 --> 00:27:29.140
to come home for a daily walk.

00:27:29.140 --> 00:27:38.660
