00:27:48.070 --> 00:27:54.120
And I turned to him
and said, "Sweetheart,

00:27:54.120 --> 00:27:56.700 position:56%
why aren't you picking up your feet?

00:27:56.700 --> 00:27:59.370
Why are you shuffling?"

00:27:59.370 --> 00:28:02.550
And he said, "I don't know."

00:28:02.550 --> 00:28:09.900
Well, then he began having a
series of automobile accidents

00:28:09.900 --> 00:28:17.090
and with those the insurance
company said after three accidents

00:28:17.090 --> 00:28:24.020
in 18 months we're
cutting out his insurance.

00:28:24.020 --> 00:28:34.770
