00:29:31.850 --> 00:29:33.150
&gt;&gt; Diane Rehm: Yeah.

00:29:33.150 --> 00:29:34.450
&gt;&gt; David M. Rubenstein:
But then what happened

00:29:34.450 --> 00:29:37.780
when he became too difficult
to medically treat him,

00:29:37.780 --> 00:29:42.310
you ultimately had to decide to
put him in an assisted living type

00:29:42.310 --> 00:29:43.630
of facility, is that right?

00:29:43.630 --> 00:29:46.440
&gt;&gt; Diane Rehm: We decided
