00:30:50.220 --> 00:30:52.130
Visiting him every
day, living alone.

00:30:52.130 --> 00:30:54.540
&gt;&gt; Diane Rehm: That's
exactly right, David.

00:30:54.540 --> 00:31:01.810
That aloneness began when he
was moved to the facility.

00:31:01.810 --> 00:31:08.670
And I can remember the very
day walking back into our condo

00:31:08.670 --> 00:31:13.910
