with John Rehm for 54 years.

00:31:38.900 --> 00:31:42.960
And now to be alone
for the first time

00:31:42.960 --> 00:31:46.160
in my life was kind of shocking.

00:31:46.160 --> 00:31:49.110
&gt;&gt; David M. Rubenstein: And
